GM May Build Plant to Make Chevrolet Cars in Turkey, HT Says

-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 
2011-08-13T11:11:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-13/gm-may-build-plant-to-make-chevrolet-cars-in-turkey-ht-says.html
General Motors Co. (GM)  may decide to
build a plant in  Turkey  that will start making  Chevrolet  cars in
2014,  Haberturk  newspaper reported, citing Tolga Atmaca, head of
Chevrolet in Turkey.  GM sold 11,735 Chevrolets in Turkey in the first six months
of this year, up 58 percent from a year earlier, the newspaper
said. Sales may reach 25,000 this year, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
 eersoy@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dick Schumacher at 
 dschumacher@bloomberg.net  